<p>加入购物车：add…to cart</p>
<p>优惠券：coupons</p>
<p>下单：place your order</p>
<p>分期付款：installment</p>
<p>有货/断货：in stock/out of stock</p>
<p>刷爆信用卡：max out the credit card</p>
<p>现金红包：cash voucher</p>
